OL,4,CChancellor Rishi Sunak under pressure
OL,5,Cover state pension rise
OL,6, The chancellor has said "fairness" will
OL,7, be the consideration as he faces
OL,8, pressure to rule out a predicted 8%
OL,9, rise in the state pension next year.
OL,11,FOfficial forecasts suggest that the
OL,12,Flink with earnings growth could mean
OL,13,Fthe bumper rise in the amount paid from
OL,14,FApril 2022.
OL,16,FRishi Sunak told the BBC a decision on
OL,17,Fpensions would be "based on fairness
OL,18,Ffor pensioners and for taxpayers".
OL,20,FVarious commentators have called for an
OL,21,Foverhaul of the rules.
